---

<BaseLayout
  title="Smart Pet Device Comparisons 2026 — Head-to-Head | SmartPetGuide"
  description="Head-to-head comparisons of popular smart pet devices. Litter-Robot 4 vs Leo's Loo Too, Furbo vs Petcube, WOPET vs Petlibro, and more."
>
  <Breadcrumb crumbs={[{ label: "Compare" }]} />

  <article>
    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold leading-tight text-forest md:text-4xl">Compare</h1>
    <p class="mt-3 text-lg leading-relaxed text-bark-muted">
      Head-to-head comparisons of the most popular smart pet devices. We break down price, features, pros/cons, and which one is right for you.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-2">
      {comparisons.map((c) => (
        <a
          href={`/compare/${c.slug}`}
          class="group rounded-2xl border border-sage-dark/30 bg-white p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        >
          <p class="font-display text-lg font-semibold text-forest transition-colors group-hover:text-honey">
            {c.title}
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-bark-muted">{c.desc}</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-3 text-sm">
            <span class="rounded-lg bg-forest/5 px-2.5 py-1 font-medium text-forest">{c.productA} — {c.priceA}</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-bark-muted">vs</span>
            <span class="rounded-lg bg-sage-light/50 px-2.5 py-1 font-medium text-forest">{c.productB} — {c.priceB}</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
